data.description: Located in the sought-after Twin Creeks development, this spacious single-story home offers 4 bedrooms and 2 baths, encompassing over 2,000 sq ft of living space. $25,000 owned 8 KW solar system. The open floorplan allows for seamless flow between the formal living and dining areas. The family room features a charming fireplace and connects to the well-appointed kitchen with stainless appliances, tile countertops, an induction range, LG Refrigerator, and a KitchenAid dishwasher. Additional highlights include a indoor laundry area, beautiful laminate flooring, plantation shutters, ceiling fans, and a new water heater. The garage includes shelves for organization. Outside, the tasteful and low-maintenance yard features mow strips and raised permit beds, creating a serene oasis.
